==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chrysophyta
<hw>Chrysophyta</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a division of mostly freshwater
eukaryotic algae having the chlorophyll masked by brown or yellow
pigment; yellow-green and golden-brown algae and diatoms, including the
Xanthophyceae, Chrysophyceae, Bacillariophyceae; some some
classification systems superseded or subsumed by
Heterokontophyta.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> division Chrysophyta.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>chrysopid</ent>⟦br⟧
